Package name.livitski.tools.xml.staxform.helpers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConditionalEventProcessor
    Examines a stream of XML events, extracts events satisfying a filter, forwards them to the target XMLEventProcessor, and includes that processor's output in the result.
    EventProcessorChain
    Combines two event processors into a chain.
    IdentityEventProcessor
    A trivial XMLEventProcessor that outputs the same sequence of events that it is fed.
    NullEventProcessor
    A processor that discards any events it receives.
